&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;
mso-bidi-font-style:italic&quot;&gt;The&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;
development hereby permitted will ensure the renewable energy infrastructure
will be carried out in accordance with document Energy Statement [Revision 01]
dated 30.06.2021 delivering a 35.05% reduction in site wide CO2 emissions, is
implemented prior to first occupation of the dwellings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;mso-layout-grid-align:none;
text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;The proposed dwellings
shall comply with the water efficiency optional requirement in paragraphs 2.8
to 2.12 of the Building Regulations Approved Document G. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;mso-layout-grid-align:none;
text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;mso-layout-grid-align:none;
text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;No demolition or hedge
clearance shall take place between March and August inclusive without a nesting
bird survey being carried out by a qualified ecologist no more than 48 hours
prior to works commencing.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;mso-layout-grid-align:none;
text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;If nesting birds are found
works must be delayed until the young have fledged. A strategy should be agreed
with the Local Planning Authority to ensure the nesting birds are not disturbed
by works taking place on the site. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;mso-layout-grid-align:none;
text-autospace:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;BodyText1&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom:12.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-style:italic&quot;&gt;The
proposed development shall achieve a Certificate of Compliance in respect of
the Secured by Design scheme, or alternatively achieve security standards
(based on Secured by Design principles) to the satisfaction of the Metropolitan
Police, details of which shall be provided to the Local Planning Authority for
its written approval prior to the first occupation of the approved development.
All security measures applied to the approved development shall be permanently
retained thereafter.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;BodyText1&quot; style=&quot;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;
margin-left:0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:
auto;margin-left:18.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;Prior to first occupation the development hereby
permitted shall be carried out in accordance with the submitted Energy
Statement [Revision 01] dated 30.06.2021 to achieve a minimum 35.05% reduction
in carbon dioxide emissions over Part L of the Building Regulations (2013).&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;Prior to first occupation,
the 73 cycle storage spaces shown on 9021/10 Proposed Ground Floor/ Site Plan
[Revision P5] dated 29.10.2021 dated 30.09.2021 and detailed in the submitted
Transport Statement dated June 2021 shall be implemented and thereafter
retained for the lifetime of the development. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

